layout: base.njk
permalink: /panels.html
title: 2022 Conference — Panel details
description: "Details of the closed-call panels for the 2022 EISS Annual Conference in Berlin: defense cooperation, military technology, private actors in war, interventions, terrorism, intelligence, arms transfers, and WMD."
metaImage: /assets/images/past-meta.jpg
navKey: ""
---

<header class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Archive · 2022 Conference</span>
    <h1>Panel details</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">
      The 2022 EISS Annual Conference featured eight closed-call panels, each chaired by a leading
      scholar. These pages are preserved as a working record of the conference programme.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="lead muted" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-6); max-width: 44rem;">
      The annual conference is the flagship of the Initiative. Below are the closed-call panels
      that featured in 2022.
    </p>

    <ol style="list-style: none; padding: 0; counter-reset: panel; display: grid; gap: var(--space-5);">
      {% for panel in panels2022 %}
      <li style="counter-increment: panel;" class="card" data-panel-number="{{ loop.index }}">
        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); align-items: baseline;">
          <span aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-2xl); font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: var(--tracking-display); min-width: 2.5rem;">{{ "0" ~ loop.index if loop.index < 10 else loop.index }}</span>
          <div style="flex: 1;">
            <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 0.8vw, var(--fs-xl)); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">{{ panel.title }}</h2>
            <p class="text-subtle" style="font-size: var(--fs-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); font-style: italic;">{{ panel.chair | replace(r/\s*\([^)]*\)/g, "") }}</p>
            <p class="muted" style="margin: 0;">{{ panel.description }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <article class="prose">
      <p class="meta">
        These panel calls are archived from the 2022 Annual Conference in Berlin.
        For information about upcoming conferences, see <a href="/past.html">all past conferences</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
